<div class="htj-steps-section page-width">
  <div class="htj-steps-grid">

    <div class="htj-step-card">
      <div class="htj-step-card__header">
        <span class="htj-step-card__num">01</span>
        <div class="htj-step-card__title-row">
          <span class="htj-step-card__label">Come &amp; Try</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="htj-step-card__body">
        <p>Experience our coaching approach first-hand with a free no-obligation session. Meet the coaches, try our training methods, and see if we're the right fit.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Free — no cost, no commitment</li>
          <li>All disciplines available on the day — sprints, hurdles, jumps, throws</li>
          <li>Coaches will assess your background and point you to the right program</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/pages/come-and-try" class="htj-step-card__btn">Register for Come &amp; Try</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="htj-step-card">
      <div class="htj-step-card__header">
        <span class="htj-step-card__num">02</span>
        <div class="htj-step-card__title-row">
          <span class="htj-step-card__label">Become a Member</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="htj-step-card__body">
        <p>Once you've attended a Come &amp; Try, choose the pass that suits your training schedule. All passes give access to every session during your period.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Single Session — $15</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Weekly Pass — $40</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Monthly Membership — $150</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Term Membership — $300</strong></li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/collections/coaching-services" class="htj-step-card__btn">View Coaching Packages</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .htj-steps-section {
    padding: 0 20px 60px;
  }

  .htj-steps-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .htj-steps-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .htj-step-card {
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    background-color: #111111;
  }

  .htj-step-card__header {
    padding: 28px 28px 24px;
    border-bottom: 4px solid #82f2b3;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .htj-step-card__num {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1;
    color: #82f2b3;
    display: block;
  }

  .htj-step-card__title-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .htj-step-card__label {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .htj-step-card__body {
    padding: 28px;
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .htj-step-card__body p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: #e0e0e0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .htj-step-card__body ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .htj-step-card__body li {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: #e0e0e0;
  }

  .htj-step-card__body strong {
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .htj-step-card__btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: #82f2b3;
    color: #0a2910;
    padding: 14px 24px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: auto;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
  }

  .htj-step-card__btn:hover {
    opacity: 0.85;
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "How to Join Steps",
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "How to Join Steps"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
